Name: Ink
URL: https://github.com/google/ink.git
Version: 1.1.0-alpha03
Revision: 4413fe7bd41f09f37d7c8fe87df59b6e0f54300a
Update Mechanism: Manual
License: Apache-2.0
License File: LICENSE
Shipped: yes
Security Critical: yes

Description:

The C++ library used in the PDF Viewer for annotating PDFs. There is another
copy in //third_party/ink, but the version here is kept in sync with the
androidx.ink.* Java libraries.

Local Modifications:

None

Update Instructions:

1) Update the version in build.gradle.template
2) Wait for the packager to run
3) Wait for the auto-roller to post a CL with the change
4) Add to the auto-roller's CL an update to this checkout:
  * Use roll_dep.py (depot_tools) to update the DEPS entry & gitlink.
  * Ask gemini to use find_required_jni.py to update the sources list.
  * Note: It does not take into account methods that R8 determines as
    unreachable. Trimming it based on R8 would be more correct, but may
    also lead to more frequent updates.
  * Update the Revision in this file.
